After putting '90 model Toyota Camry seats in our 76 we had the same
[problem.  Solved it with a typist foot stool which is about 25mm  
(1") high
at the front & about 100 mm (4") high at the back.  Just the right  
angle for
comfortable foot placement for the passenger.

